## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-102">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache> 类提高复杂的呈现性能 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-102">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache> class to improve rendering performance of a complex <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-103">创建一个 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache> 并将其分配给的 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CacheMode%2A> 属性， <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> 以便在视频内存中将元素及其子树缓存为位图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-103">Create a <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache> and assign it to the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CacheMode%2A> property of a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> to cache the element and its subtree as a bitmap in video memory.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-104">当你需要尽快对进行动画处理、转换或缩放时，此方法非常有用 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-104">This is useful when you need to animate, translate, or scale a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> as quickly as possible.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-105">此方法可在缓存内容时实现性能和视觉质量之间的权衡。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-105">This approach enables a tradeoff between performance and visual quality while content is cached.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-106">使用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCacheBrush> 类可有效重复使用缓存的元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-106">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCacheBrush> class to efficiently reuse a cached element.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-107">设置 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.RenderAtScale%2A> 属性以缩放位图缓存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-107">Set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.RenderAtScale%2A> property to scale the bitmap cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-108">如果要缩放元素，并且希望元素呈现得更清晰，而不是只是在元素的本机分辨率下生成缓存，则这种方法很有用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-108">This is useful if an element will be zoomed, and you want the element to render more clearly than it would if the cache were simply generated at the element's native resolution.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-109"><xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.SnapsToDevicePixels%2A>当缓存显示需要像素对齐才能正确呈现的内容（如 ClearType 文本）时，请设置属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-109">Set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.SnapsToDevicePixels%2A> property when the cache displays content that requires pixel-alignment to render correctly, such as ClearType text.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-110">和类将忽略此属性 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCacheBrush> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Viewport2DVisual3D> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-110">This property is ignored by the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCacheBrush> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Viewport2DVisual3D> classes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-111">缓存控件不会影响鼠标悬停行为，因此，按下鼠标进行命中测试的操作就好像位图是实时控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-111">Caching a control does not affect mouse-over behavior, so mouse-over hit testing operates as if it the bitmap were a live control.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-112">仅在 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> 或其子树的结构发生更改时，或在设置更改时才会重新生成缓存 <xref:System.Windows.Media.CacheMode> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-112">Cache regeneration occurs only when the structure of the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> or its subtree changes, or when the <xref:System.Windows.Media.CacheMode> settings change.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-113">设置 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.RenderAtScale%2A> 或 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.EnableClearType%2A> 属性会导致重新生成缓存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-113">Setting the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.RenderAtScale%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.EnableClearType%2A> properties causes cache regeneration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-114">对缓存的父可视化树（ <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> 如转换、缩放、opacities 和效果）的更改不会影响缓存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-114">Changes to the parent visual tree of the cached <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>, such as transforms, scales, opacities, and effects, do not affect the cache.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-115">硬件加速功能不可用时的缓存功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-115">The cache functions when hardware acceleration is not available.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-116">在这种情况下，位图是在软件中呈现的，最大位图尺寸为 2048 x 2048。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-116">In this case, the bitmap is rendered in software, and the maximum bitmap dimensions are 2048 x 2048.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="c420f-117"><xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions> 和不 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextOptions> 通过缓存元素传播。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-117"><xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextOptions> do not propagate through a cached element.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c420f-118">可能需要在缓存下的子元素中再次设置这些选项。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-118">You may have to set these options again in child elements below the cache.</span></span>  
  
   
  
