## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-137">设置 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.EnableClearType%2A> 属性以允许在缓存中呈现 ClearType 文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-137">Set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.EnableClearType%2A> property to allow ClearType text to be rendered in the cache.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c420f-138">当 <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.EnableClearType%2A> 属性为时 `true` ，应用程序必须在不透明背景上呈现其所有 ClearType 文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c420f-138">When the <xref:System.Windows.Media.BitmapCache.EnableClearType%2A> property is `true`, your application must render all of its ClearType text on an opaque background.</span></span>  
  
